{
  "video_id": "N0xBmtXLaTs",
  "title": "Financial Statements - Lecture 9 - The notes to the financial statements - IFRS & ASPE",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 11370.0,
      "end_time": 12260.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12260.0,
      "end_time": 13200.0,
      "text": "Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 13200.0,
      "end_time": 15270.0,
      "text": "And in this video, we&#39;ll be exploring the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15270.0,
      "end_time": 16789.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16789.0,
      "end_time": 18330.0,
      "text": "The notes to the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 20910.0,
      "text": "are not considered a financial statement per se."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20910.0,
      "end_time": 23010.0,
      "text": "But they are an important and integral part"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23010.0,
      "end_time": 24390.0,
      "text": "of the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24390.0,
      "end_time": 26370.0,
      "text": "This is true for public corporations, who"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26370.0,
      "end_time": 29400.0,
      "text": "must use IFRS, and private corporations, who"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29400.0,
      "end_time": 30920.0,
      "text": "choose to use IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30920.0,
      "end_time": 32970.0,
      "text": "In addition, private corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 32970.0,
      "end_time": 34770.0,
      "text": "can choose to follow ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34770.0,
      "end_time": 37020.0,
      "text": "If they do, they produce a slightly different set"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 37020.0,
      "end_time": 38530.0,
      "text": "of financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38530.0,
      "end_time": 40320.0,
      "text": "Companies following ASPE are also"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40320.0,
      "end_time": 43560.0,
      "text": "required to include notes to the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43560.0,
      "end_time": 46350.0,
      "text": "In these videos, I&#39;ll be using a public corporation"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46350.0,
      "end_time": 49920.0,
      "text": "to explain what the notes to the financial statements include."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49920.0,
      "end_time": 51840.0,
      "text": "But this video will apply to companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51840.0,
      "end_time": 54201.0,
      "text": "following IFRS or ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 54201.0,
      "end_time": 55575.0,
      "text": "In order to demonstrate the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 55575.0,
      "end_time": 57150.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements, I&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 57150.0,
      "end_time": 60300.0,
      "text": "decided to use Dollarama Inc.&#39;s annual report for the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60300.0,
      "end_time": 63000.0,
      "text": "ended February 2, 2014."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 63000.0,
      "end_time": 64739.0,
      "text": "If you download the annual report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 64739.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67020.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see that at the bottom of each of the four"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 67020.0,
      "end_time": 68790.0,
      "text": "major financial, statements, there"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 68790.0,
      "end_time": 70410.0,
      "text": "is the following statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 70410.0,
      "end_time": 72690.0,
      "text": "The accompanying notes are an integral part"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 72690.0,
      "end_time": 75460.0,
      "text": "of these consolidated financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 75460.0,
      "end_time": 77760.0,
      "text": "This is a warning to users."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 77760.0,
      "end_time": 80130.0,
      "text": "A failure to read the notes to the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 80130.0,
      "end_time": 82650.0,
      "text": "will result in incomplete knowledge of the company&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 82650.0,
      "end_time": 84000.0,
      "text": "financial health."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 84000.0,
      "end_time": 86370.0,
      "text": "The notes supplement the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 86370.0,
      "end_time": 89040.0,
      "text": "Without them, it&#39;s not possible to fully understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 89040.0,
      "end_time": 91380.0,
      "text": "the financial condition of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 91380.0,
      "end_time": 93660.0,
      "text": "The notes should include any information"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 93660.0,
      "end_time": 95580.0,
      "text": "that will improve the user&#39;s understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 95580.0,
      "end_time": 97170.0,
      "text": "of the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 97170.0,
      "end_time": 100110.0,
      "text": "Although there are some choices as to what the notes should"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 100110.0,
      "end_time": 102390.0,
      "text": "include, there are three basic types"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 102390.0,
      "end_time": 104670.0,
      "text": "of notes that have to be included."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 104670.0,
      "end_time": 107130.0,
      "text": "First is a statement of compliance, indicating"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 107130.0,
      "end_time": 109440.0,
      "text": "the use of either IFRS or ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 109440.0,
      "end_time": 111720.0,
      "text": "Since Dollarama is a public corporation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 111720.0,
      "end_time": 114900.0,
      "text": "their compliance statement references the use of IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114900.0,
      "end_time": 117930.0,
      "text": "This note is called the basis of preparation note,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117930.0,
      "end_time": 120720.0,
      "text": "and it must be included in every financial statements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 120720.0,
      "end_time": 123420.0,
      "text": "whether using IFRS or ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123420.0,
      "end_time": 126540.0,
      "text": "Next is a summary of significant accounting policies and rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126540.0,
      "end_time": 128889.0,
      "text": "used to prepare the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 128889.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133290.0,
      "text": "Again, this is required, whether a company follows IFRS or ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 133290.0,
      "end_time": 134820.0,
      "text": "This note will include such things"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 134820.0,
      "end_time": 137670.0,
      "text": "as the basis of measurement for specific financial assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 137670.0,
      "end_time": 140850.0,
      "text": "and liabilities, how property, plant, and equipment is valued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 140850.0,
      "end_time": 142650.0,
      "text": "plus many other items."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 142650.0,
      "end_time": 145500.0,
      "text": "For Dollarama, the summary of significant accounting policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 145500.0,
      "end_time": 147600.0,
      "text": "goes on for nine pages."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 147600.0,
      "end_time": 150090.0,
      "text": "This indicates the importance of this section of the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 150090.0,
      "end_time": 152140.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 152140.0,
      "end_time": 154170.0,
      "text": "The third type of note disclosure"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 154170.0,
      "end_time": 156930.0,
      "text": "is the relevant information to aid a user&#39;s understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 156930.0,
      "end_time": 158940.0,
      "text": "of individual line items reported"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 158940.0,
      "end_time": 161500.0,
      "text": "on the face of the four financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 161500.0,
      "end_time": 163580.0,
      "text": "For instance, in Dollarama&#39;s notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 163580.0,
      "end_time": 166800.0,
      "text": "note seven gives details of the property and equipment that"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 166800.0,
      "end_time": 168990.0,
      "text": "is listed under non-current assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 168990.0,
      "end_time": 171240.0,
      "text": "on the statement of financial position."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 171240.0,
      "end_time": 173550.0,
      "text": "Each line item from the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 173550.0,
      "end_time": 176610.0,
      "text": "that does have a note is cross-referenced to that note,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 176610.0,
      "end_time": 179700.0,
      "text": "in order to help users locate the relevant information."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 179700.0,
      "end_time": 182220.0,
      "text": "There are other notes that may also be included,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 182220.0,
      "end_time": 185790.0,
      "text": "such as any disclosures that are required by specific standards"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 185790.0,
      "end_time": 187440.0,
      "text": "or notes about items that are not"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 187440.0,
      "end_time": 189030.0,
      "text": "listed on the statements themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 189030.0,
      "end_time": 191520.0,
      "text": "such as exposure to significant risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 191520.0,
      "end_time": 194080.0,
      "text": "Although some notes are specifically required,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 194080.0,
      "end_time": 197160.0,
      "text": "IFRS and ASPE have a more general requirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 197160.0,
      "end_time": 198960.0,
      "text": "that notes be provided for anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 198960.0,
      "end_time": 201420.0,
      "text": "that would allow a user to better understand the company&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 201420.0,
      "end_time": 202909.0,
      "text": "financial health."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 202909.0,
      "end_time": 204700.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s check your understanding of the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 204700.0,
      "end_time": 207020.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 207020.0,
      "end_time": 211970.0,
      "text": "On April 9, 2014, Dollarama announced a 14% increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 211970.0,
      "end_time": 213710.0,
      "text": "in their quarterly dividend."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 213710.0,
      "end_time": 216350.0,
      "text": "This announcement was made after the February 2"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 216350.0,
      "end_time": 218150.0,
      "text": "financial statement date."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218150.0,
      "end_time": 220925.0,
      "text": "Where, if at all, would this information be reported?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225900.0,
      "end_time": 227610.0,
      "text": "Even though the increase in the dividend"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227610.0,
      "end_time": 230340.0,
      "text": "was announced after the date of the financial statements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 230340.0,
      "end_time": 232860.0,
      "text": "it is a subsequent event that is important for the users"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 232860.0,
      "end_time": 235410.0,
      "text": "to know, in order to better understand the financial health"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 235410.0,
      "end_time": 236640.0,
      "text": "of Dollarama."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 236640.0,
      "end_time": 238800.0,
      "text": "As such, it&#39;s not included in the face of any"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 238800.0,
      "end_time": 240270.0,
      "text": "of the financial statements, but it"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 240270.0,
      "end_time": 243720.0,
      "text": "must be included in the notes to the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 243720.0,
      "end_time": 245520.0,
      "text": "The purpose of the notes is clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 245520.0,
      "end_time": 248100.0,
      "text": "Notes explain and expand on the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 248100.0,
      "end_time": 250570.0,
      "text": "provided on the face of the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250570.0,
      "end_time": 252660.0,
      "text": "Companies are responsible for fully disclosing"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 252660.0,
      "end_time": 254920.0,
      "text": "all relevant information for decision making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 254920.0,
      "end_time": 257629.0,
      "text": "and the notes are a critical part of this responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 257629.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259170.00000000003,
      "text": "The notes to the financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 259170.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262500.0,
      "text": "include both qualitative and quantitative information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 262500.0,
      "end_time": 265860.0,
      "text": "whatever is required to improve users&#39; understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 265860.0,
      "end_time": 268530.0,
      "text": "In fact, the notes include so much information"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 268530.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "that they make up the majority of the financial report."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273660.0,
      "text": "For instance, in Dollarama&#39;s annual report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 273660.0,
      "end_time": 275580.0,
      "text": "there are only four pages dedicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 275580.0,
      "end_time": 277410.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277410.0,
      "end_time": 280440.0,
      "text": "but there are 25 pages of notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280440.0,
      "end_time": 282231.0,
      "text": "Investors, lenders, and creditors"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282231.0,
      "end_time": 284730.0,
      "text": "use the notes to increase their understanding of the content"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 284730.0,
      "end_time": 287310.0,
      "text": "of the financial statements, so they can better understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 287310.0,
      "end_time": 289460.0,
      "text": "the health of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289460.0,
      "end_time": 290900.0,
      "text": "We have now completed our lectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 290900.0,
      "end_time": 292100.0,
      "text": "on the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 292100.0,
      "end_time": 294410.0,
      "text": "But likely, you, a student of accounting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 294410.0,
      "end_time": 296900.0,
      "text": "have an even more important question."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 296900.0,
      "end_time": 298280.0,
      "text": "What are the steps you should use"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 298280.0,
      "end_time": 302150.0,
      "text": "to attack a financial statement question on a test or an exam?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 302150.0,
      "end_time": 305500.0,
      "text": "And that is the subject of our next video."
    }
  ]
}